						<div class="postbody">In my emulator, after $00F8 is set to $08, I get a ton of $2002 reads, then one per frame as it synchronizes exactly to the PPU, then the read at 89341 PPU clocks after VBL that suppresses VBL before $01 is written to $00F8.
